Note: 2001-12-16: Dibang Valley district split into Lower Dibang Valley and Upper Dibang Valley.
Kamrup Metropolitan district split from Kamrup; Baksa district formed from parts of Barpeta, Nalbari, and Kamrup; Chirang district formed from parts of Barpeta, Bongaigaon, and Kokrajhar.
Udalguri district formed from parts of Darrang and Sonitpur.
Dantewada district split into Bijapur and Dakshin Bastar Dantewada
2000-04-01: Kurung Kumey district split from Lower Subansiri.
Samba district formed from parts of Jammu and Kathua
Seraikela district split from Pashchim Singhbhum
Ramanagara district split from Bangalore Rural
Burhanpur district split from Khandwa (East Nimar)
Kiphire and Longleng districts split from Tuensang
Tarn Taran district split from Amritsar
Mohali district formed from parts of Patiala and Rupnagar
Pratapgarh formed from parts of Banswara, Chittorgarh, and Udaipur
Tiruppur district formed from parts of Coimbatore and Erode
Kanshi Ram Nagar split from Etah
Midnapore district split into East Midnapore and West Midnapore
